for some reason git doesn't use EDITOR in Kubuntu(bash), just do:
    git config --global core.editor "vim"

---

setting up gitosis:
-per http://www.ivankuznetsov.com/2010/05/setting-up-your-own-git-server-on-ubuntu.html

    (install gitosis w/ GUI or sudo apt-get install gitosis)
    sudo -H -u gitosis gitosis-init <~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
